quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  40,10,"Mazima abo abaakafuwala balikowoolwa (nga bali mu muliro nti) mazima obusungu bwa Katonda busuffu okusinga okwesunguwalira kwa mmwe, bwe mwakowolwanga okujja eri obukkiriza (wabula ate mmwe) nemuwakanya"
  40,11,"Baligamba nti ayi Mukama omulabirizi waffe watutta emirundi ebiri notuwa obulamu emirundi ebiri, kaakano tukkirizza ebyonoono byaffe (bitusaanidde), abaffe waliwo ekkubo lyonna eritufulumya mu muliro"
  40,12,"(Baligambwa nti) ekyo mmwe (kye mulimu) buli Katonda lweyasabwanga yekka nga muwakanya, ate buli lwe yagattibwangako ekintu ekirala olwo nga mukkiriza, kale nno okulamula (olwaleero) kwa Katonda (yekka) owa waggulu owekitiibwa"
  40,13,Yye yooyo abalaga obubonero bwe era abassiza amazzi okuva waggulu nga riziki (gye muli) naye teyebulirira (nabyo) okugyako oyo adda eri (Katonda)
  40,14,Kale musabe Katonda ng’eddiini mugikola ku lulwe yekka newakubadde nga abakafiiri bakitamwa
  40,15,"(Katonda oyo) ow'ebitiibwa ebya waggulu nannyini Arish, assa obubaka okusinziira ku kiragiro kye kwoyo gwaba ayagadde mu baddu be, abe nga atiisa (abantu ebiribaawo ku) lunaku lw'okusisinkana"
  40,16,"Olunaku bo (abantu) bonna lwe balyeyoleka )mu maaso ga Katonda) tewali kintu kyonna kyava mu bo kiryekweka Katonda, (balibuuzibwa nti) obufuzi bwani olwaleero? (olwo nno nebategezebwa nti) bwa Katonda ali omu nantalemwa"
  40,17,"Olwaleero buli mwoyo gugenda kusasulwa olwebyo bye gwakola tewali kulyazamanya olwaleero, mazima Katonda mwangu wa kubala"
  40,18,"Batiise (gwe nabbi Muhammad) olunaku olusembedde, ekiseera emitima lwegiribeera mu malokooli (olw'entiisa) nga banyikaavu, abeeyisa obubi tebagenda kuba na ffa nfe, wadde muwolereza ayinza okuwulirizibwa"
  40,19,(Anti) Katonda amanyi amaaso agatali meesimbu era nga bwamanyi ebyo ebifuba bye bikweka
  40,20,"Era Katonda alamula mazima, bo abo abasaba ebintu ebirala nebaleka Katonda, tebalina kintu kyonna kye balamula (nekiba kyo). Mazima Katonda ye yaawulira ennyo alaba"